### Example 1: Create an new instance of PsApiManagementSslSetting to Enable TLSv 1.0 in both Frontend (between client and APIM) and Backend (between APIM and Backend) of ApiManagement Gateway. (autogenerated)
```powershell
PS C:\> New-AzApiManagementSslSetting -BackendProtocol $enableTls -FrontendProtocol $enableTls
```
